STC (Standard Template Construct)
=================================

This project includes data and assets derived from third-party sources. The
recipe-pack artifacts under data/aef/ (recipe-pack.json, recipe-pack.i18n.json)
are extracted from the upstream source listed below. The upstream commit the
snapshot was taken from is recorded in vendor/endfield-calc/SOURCE.json and in
each artifact's source block.

The planner application does not link, embed, or import third-party source code
at runtime; third-party material is consumed only as game data and icons.

